characteristic.__text: Re-roll hit rolls of 1 made for friendly GELLERPOX INFECTED units within 6" of Vulgrar Thrice-Cursed.
Vulgrar Thrice-Cursed has a 5+ invulnerable save.
This weapon automatically hits its target.

Models in this unit have a 5+ invulnerable save. Each time you roll an unmodified saving throw of 6 for this model in the Fight phase, the unit that made the attack suffers 1 mortal wound after it has made all of its attacks.
Models in this unit have a 5+ invulnerable save.
Models in this unit only receive the benefit of their Disgustingly Resilient ability against attacks with a Damage characteristic of 1.
Subtract 1 from hit rolls made for attacks with ranged weapons that target this unit.
Re-roll wound rolls of 1 for this weapon.
Re-roll wound rolls of 1 for this weapon.
You can re-roll failed charge rolls for this unit. In addition, whenever this unit piles in or consolidates, it can move up to 6" instead of 3".
Each unmodified hit roll of 6 made for an attack with this weapon scores 2 hits.
Subtract 1 from hit rolls for attacks that target this unit.
Add 1 slain model to this unit at the start of every turn.
Each unmodified hit roll of 6 made for this weapon automatically results in a wound (do not make a wound roll for that attack).
Roll a D6 each time a model in this unit is slain in the Fight phase; on a 6 the unit that killed the model suffers a mortal wound after it has made all its attacks.
If your army is battle-forged, you receive 3 additional Command Points. These can only be spent to use Gellerpox Infected Stratagems.

rule.description: This ability has no effect unless your army includes VULGRAR THRICE-CURSED. If it does, you cannot set up any units with this ability before you have set up VULGRAR THRICE-CURSED. When you set up VULGRAR THRICE-CURSED during deployment, all units with this ability are set up at the same time. When you set up VULGRAR THRICE-CURSED on the battlefield for the first time, all units with this ability must be set up within 6" of him. If they cannot be set up, they count as destroyed.

characteristic.__text: Roll a D6 each time a model with this ability loses a wound; on a 5+ that model does not lose that wound.
Subtract 1 from the Leadership characteristic of units whilst they are within 6" of any enemy models with this ability.
This unit does not take up a slot in a Detachment that includes Vulgrar Thrice-Cursed.
